import React from 'react';
import { Box } from '../components/Box';
import { Flex } from '../components/Flex';
import { Text } from '../components/Text';

function Home() {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Flex>
        <Box
          css={{
            padding: '$5 $6',
            display: 'grid',
            gap: '$3',
            gridTemplateColumns: 'repeat(3, max-content)',
            // gridTemplateRows: 'repeat(9, max-content)',
            gridAutoRows: 'max-content',
            alignItems: 'baseline',
            textAlign: 'center',
          }}
        >
          <Text size="9">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="9">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="9">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="8">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="8">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="8">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="7">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="7">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="7">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="6">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="6">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="6">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="5">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="5">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="5">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="4">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="4">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="4">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="3">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="3">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="3">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="2">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="2">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="2">Cc</Text>

          <Text size="1">Aa</Text>
          <Text size="1">Bb</Text>
          <Text size="1">Cc</Text>
        </Box>
      </Flex>
      <Box
        css={{
          padding: '$5 $6',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          gap: '$3',
        }}
      >
        <Text size="5" weight="regular">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
        <Text size="5" weight="medium">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
        <Text size="5" weight="semibold">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
        <Text size="5" weight="bold">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Home;
